name: MechMinds
description:
MechMinds is the first delationary project to combine AI x Blockchain with OpenAI's GPT. Currently leveraging GPT4.

Our AI [Chatbot](https://www.mechminds.ai/chat) lets you talk with your NFT. [Merge](https://www.mechminds.ai/merge) MechMinds to make them smarter & creates a new generative AI NFT. The [supply]( https://www.mechminds.ai/stats) deflates as MechMinds are merged. 

Current Supply <8192 MechMind robots.
